{"word":"G1801 - ἐνωτίζομαι - enōtízomai - en-o-tid'-zom-ahee - Hearken","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνωτίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enōtízomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-o-tid'-zom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hearken</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - செவிகொடு"},{"paragraph":"to receive into the ear; give ear to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from a compound of <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G3775 - οὖς - oûs - ooce/3775\">G3775</a>; to take <i>in one's ear</i>, that is, to <i>listen:</i> - hearken.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1801/1801\">G1801</a>, <a href=\"#/G3775/3775\">G3775</a>, <a href=\"#/G5621/5621\">G5621</a>"}]}